Description:
    Generates everything need for a new resource with
    CafeCar: model, routes, controller, policy, and a migration.

Example:
    `bin/rails generate cafe_car:resource admin/invoices`

        This creates:
            Model:      app/models/invoice.rb
            Migration:  db/migrations/xxx_create_invoices.rb
            Routes:     resources :invoices, namespace: :admin
            Controller: app/controllers/admin/invoices_controller.rb
            Policy:     app/policies/invoice_policy.rb
